  <Fragment slot="lead">
    <p class="text-center text-sm md:px-16 md:text-lg"> Hello! My name is Adithya Krishna Eemani, as a highly motivated individual currently pursuing a B.Tech degree in Computer Science and Engineering with a specialization 
